originalText.text:
My experience with Dr Park and Ana has been positive. The office environment is quiet, clean and there is no wait time. Dr Park was referred to me by my previous primary and she is nothing but an exceptional doctor who listens to her patients, genuinely cares, responds to txt msg and emails instantly, professional  and you can tell she loves her job.
Recovering from COVID-19 and having lingering symptoms , Dr Park is not judgmental ,offers her whole self and assures me that all will be well.
She is amazing and will recommend her.

originalText.text: After moving to New York City, I wanted to establish care with a doctor who would listen to what I had to say and work to resolve any issues I was having. Making my appointment with Dr. Park was the best decision I could have made. She is kind, personable and genuinely cares about the health and well-being of her patients. Her office is clean, bright and the staff is fantastic! My wait time was short and the process of booking an appointment was quick and easy. If you’re looking for a primary care doctor in NYC, or just someone to consult with about a health issue then look no further!

originalText.text:
I love Dr. Park!
I have been seeing her for over 5 years. Now it is farther for me to see her but I still make the trip as it is worth it. Visits do not feel rushed. She takes the time to get to know you and your medical history and makes thorough notes. If I ever have a question, I can e-mail her or her assistant and get a response in a timely manner.

originalText.text: I’ve been a patient of Dr. Park’s since Summer 2018, and throughout this time, she has demonstrated nothing less than exceptional knowledge and skills, in addition to a warm, comforting bedside manner. Within telehealth or in-person appointments (felt fully safe and protected during the COVID pandemic), she demonstrates sound medical knowledge and clinical judgement. Something I have yet to find in another PCP is that she is takes earnest interest in my worries and concerns, and tries to problem solve ways to resolve the concerns with me in a collaborative, non-judgmental way. She goes above and beyond!!! Also, shout out to Ana! The two of them are a warm, diligent, and thorough team.
